  "name": "Suppress Curse",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/skills/green_13.jpg",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<strong>Shaman Hex</strong><br/><br/><p>As a standard action, a benefactor can attempt to suppress one curse effect that is affecting a creature or object with a touch. This functions as per remove curse, except the curse's effects are suppressed for 1 hour, even if it is a cursed shield, weapon, or suit of armor. This allows a creature afflicted with any such cursed item to remove or get rid of it. The benefactor uses her shaman level as her caster level for the purpose of this hex.</p>",
